<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8" />
<title>Template Import Soal - Word</title>
<style>
  table { border-collapse: collapse; width: 100%; margin-bottom:20px; }
  td, th { border: 1px solid #000; padding:8px; vertical-align: top; }
  .key { width: 20%; font-weight: bold; }
</style>
</head>
<body>
  <h1>Template Import Soal (Word table)</h1>
  <p>Gunakan satu tabel per soal. Kolom kiri adalah kunci (Key), kolom kanan adalah nilai (Value).</p>

  <table>
    <tr><td class="key">Type</td><td>multiple_choice</td></tr>
    <tr><td class="key">Question</td><td>Siapa proklamator Indonesia?</td></tr>
    <tr><td class="key">Answers</td><td>
      <table>
        <tr><td>A) Soekarno</td></tr>
        <tr><td>B) Hatta</td></tr>
        <tr><td>C) Soekarno-Hatta</td></tr>
        <tr><td>D) BJ Habibie</td></tr>
      </table>
    </td></tr>
    <tr><td class="key">Correct</td><td>C</td></tr>
    <tr><td class="key">Points</td><td>10</td></tr>
  </table>

  <table>
    <tr><td class="key">Type</td><td>true_false</td></tr>
    <tr><td class="key">Question</td><td>Matahari terbit dari barat.</td></tr>
    <tr><td class="key">Correct</td><td>Salah</td></tr>
    <tr><td class="key">Points</td><td>5</td></tr>
  </table>

  <table>
    <tr><td class="key">Type</td><td>essay</td></tr>
    <tr><td class="key">Question</td><td>Jelaskan proses fotosintesis.</td></tr>
    <tr><td class="key">Points</td><td>15</td></tr>
  </table>

  <table>
    <tr><td class="key">Type</td><td>multiple_choice</td></tr>
    <tr><td class="key">Question</td><td>Perhatikan gambar berikut:<br/><img src="https://via.placeholder.com/300x200.png" alt="contoh"/></td></tr>
    <tr><td class="key">Answers</td><td>
      <table>
        <tr><td>A) Opsi satu</td></tr>
        <tr><td>B) Opsi dua</td></tr>
        <tr><td>C) Opsi tiga</td></tr>
        <tr><td>D) Opsi empat</td></tr>
      </table>
    </td></tr>
    <tr><td class="key">Correct</td><td>A</td></tr>
    <tr><td class="key">Points</td><td>8</td></tr>
  </table>

  <p>Catatan: Anda dapat menyisipkan gambar langsung ke sel Question (Word akan embed gambar) atau gunakan URL gambar di dalam sel.</p>
</body>
</html>